## Bundled Files

ONNX model weights (under `onnx/PP-OCRv4/`):

- `onnx/PP-OCRv4/det/ch_PP-OCRv4_det_mobile.onnx` — Chinese PP-OCRv4 text detection (mobile)
- `onnx/PP-OCRv4/det/en_PP-OCRv3_det_mobile.onnx` — English PP-OCRv3 text detection (mobile)
- `onnx/PP-OCRv4/cls/ch_ppocr_mobile_v2.0_cls_mobile.onnx` — PP-OCR v2.0 text-direction classifier (mobile)
- `onnx/PP-OCRv4/rec/ch_PP-OCRv4_rec_mobile.onnx` — Chinese PP-OCRv4 text recognition (mobile)
- `onnx/PP-OCRv4/rec/en_PP-OCRv4_rec_mobile.onnx` — English PP-OCRv4 text recognition (mobile)

Character dictionaries (under `paddle/PP-OCRv4/`):

- `paddle/PP-OCRv4/rec/ch_PP-OCRv4_rec_mobile/ppocr_keys_v1.txt` — Chinese recognition character dictionary
- `paddle/PP-OCRv4/rec/en_PP-OCRv4_rec_mobile/en_dict.txt` — English recognition character dictionary

